fees.description: BPay payments incur a $2.50 (inc GST) fee per transaction.
A surcharge applies to all American Express and Diners Club card payments. Payments made via MasterCard or Visa do not incur any surcharge.
Dishonoured Payment fee of $9.50 (inc GST) may apply to payments we attempt that are subsequently declined.
A $55.00 (inc GST) fee may apply when we request to energise a property, or if you require a meter reading for any purpose.
A $55.00 (inc GST) fee may apply when we request to de-energise a property, or if you require a meter reading for any purpose.
A $55.00 (inc GST) fee may apply each time you request a reconnection after disconnection for non-payment.

electricityContract.terms: See our full terms and conditions at www.dodo.com/energy/terms-prices-and-regulatory-information. If you are eligible, you can apply to receive NSW Government energy rebates when you sign up with us.
electricityContract.variation: We may vary your rates and charges by providing you notice of any changes at least 5 business days before the change is effective and in any event no later than your next bill such as for tariff reassignments.

incentives.description: From time to time, Dodo Power & Gas may provide promotional offers (including one-off payments and/or products) though promotional codes, which may be redeemed when signing up. These codes do not change the rates, fees or charges of this offer.

timeOfUseRates.description: 7am to 2pm & 8pm to 10pm business days, & 7am to 10pm non-business days

greenPowerCharges.description: $0.099 per kWh (inc GST) - Electricity equal to 10% of your usage is sourced from GreenPower. Any discounts do not apply to GreenPower.
$0.099 per kWh (inc GST) - Electricity equal to 100% of your usage is sourced from GreenPower. Any discounts do not apply to GreenPower.

solarFeedInTariff.description: Retailer Feed-in Tariff (net & gross) - This plan is available to eligible small solar customers with a maximum 10kW panel size and an inverter system no greater than 10kW as part of an ongoing contract.

electricityContract.onExpiryDescription: No Term contracts do not expire until you notify us in accordance with our Energy Market Contract Terms and Conditions.
electricityContract.additionalFeeInformation: For further details on the information and fees presented, or the terms and conditions of the contract, please visit www.dodo.com/energy/terms-prices-and-regulatory-information or contact us on 13 dodo (13 36 36).
